Package: RcppTN
Type: Package
Title: Rcpp-based Truncated Normal Distribution RNG and Family
Version: 0.1-3
Date: 2013-12-02
Author: Jonathan Olmsted
Maintainer: Jonathan Olmsted <jpolmsted@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides R-level and C++-level functionality
	     to generate random deviates from and calculate moments of a 
	     Truncated Normal distribution using the Robert (1995) algorithm.
	     No d/p/q functions are provided. Functions for calculating draws 
	     and moments are provided at both levels.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: Rcpp (>= 0.10.2)
Suggests: knitr (>= 1.1), ggplot2, msm, truncnorm, testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
VignetteBuilder: knitr

